&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for a Ward Manager at Bluebell Ward, St Martins hospital Canterbury.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bluebell Ward is a busy 18 bed acute admissions ward based in Canterbury Kent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced, motivated, patient and staff centred qualified Nurse Band 7 ward Manager to maintain the high quality care delivery Bluebell Ward already provides, and support innovation and development. It is essential that you have leadership experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
